snippet.title: Taylor Momsen Admits She's a Satanist - Burns Bibles with Cigarette Butts

localized.description:
Gossip Girl Star Taylor Momsen is also the singer in the rock band The Pretty Reckless, and in their song Heaven Knows, Bibles are burned and cigarettes put out on them.  Taylor Momsen also has been photographed wearing a shirt that reads I'll fuck for Satan.  Review by Mark Dice.
